---
title: Tex-Mex Chipotle Beef & Pork Meatballs with Creamy Charred Corn Slaw
description: Tex-Mex spices and chipotle, sure sounds like a perfect pairing to us. They’re guaranteed to be crowned best flavour combo by
joining beef and pork meatballs in a colourful slaw bowl. This dish will be going steady in your weekly dinner repertoire for sure.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
